  "method": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat and add the onion and bell pepper. Sauté until the onion is translucent, about 10 to 15 minutes.",
    "Add the tomatoes, carrots, tomato paste, and ½ cup of water. Add the spices and herbs. Bring to a boil, cover, and turn down to simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "Add the kidney beans and corn. Cook on a low simmer for another 15 minutes."
  ],
